theorem closure_interior_complement_eq_complement_interior_closure
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    closure (interior ((Aᶜ) : Set X)) =
      (interior (closure (A : Set X)))ᶜ := by
  have h₁ :
      interior ((Aᶜ) : Set X) = (closure (A : Set X))ᶜ :=
    interior_complement_eq_complement_closure (A := A)
  have h₂ :
      closure ((closure (A : Set X))ᶜ) =
        (interior (closure (A : Set X)))ᶜ :=
    closure_complement_eq_complement_interior
      (A := closure (A : Set X))
  simpa [h₁] using h₂

theorem closure_complement_eq_complement_interior {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    closure ((Aᶜ) : Set X) = (interior (A : Set X))ᶜ := by
  simpa using closure_compl_eq_complement_interior (A := A)
